data.description: This stunning custom built home will wow you the moment you pull in the driveway. Once you enter the door you'll notice the attention to detail of the wrought iron railing, lighted staircase, beautiful molding and trim, and hardwood flooring. On the main level you'll find a family room with gas fireplace and a gourmet kitchen with granite counters, pecan cabinetry, and stainless steel appliances with a gas range that will make any chef happy. The dining area is large with vaulted celling and beautiful wainscoting for all of your family meals. The primary bedroom with en-suite bath features a barn door, dual vanities, and a wonderful walk-in tiled shower with glass doors. A nice walk-in closet with a closet system in place. There are two additional bedrooms on the opposite side of this level which share a jack and jill bath. You'll find a fantastic screened in porch off the family room leading to a deck area that has a staircase to the fenced in backyard for your pets or children. On the deck you'll find a Weber NG stainless grill, which conveys. Downstairs is a den with stone fireplace and gas logs, a large storage closet, a bonus room that can be used as a home office or a 4th bedroom when needed, and a full bath. The 2 car garage with utility sink is oversized with space for storage or a work bench. This home has spray foam insulation and low utility bills. This is a smart home with an Apple Home kit for controlling all lights, HVAC, and garage doors. Solid wood interior doors, Anderson windows, gas HVAC and water heater, and low voltage exterior lighting. Don't miss this opportunity! Buyer/Buyer's Agent to verify any and all info.
